e: 97B.","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:01:02.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550234653421632"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"author_id":"113598297","id":"2040550191900590085","text":"うーーーん、やっぱりclaude codeはghosttyが一番よく動くなん案でだろ","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:51.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550191900590085"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":10},"entities":{"mentions":[{"start":131,"end":143,"username":"AnthropicAI","id":"1353836358901501952"}],"urls":[{"start":280,"end":303,"url":"https://t.co/yQIhftO0Kl","expanded_url":"https://x.com/vivilinsv/status/2040550139853684832/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/yQIhftO0Kl","media_key":"3_2040550137274220544"}]},"author_id":"2238470792","id":"2040550139853684832","text":"The center of gravity in AI just shifted — from models that talk to systems that act.\n\nAgentic AI is no longer a research concept. @AnthropicAI's Claude Code hit a $1 billion run-rate within six months. Global AI venture funding reached $300 billion in Q1 2026 alone, and roughly https://t.co/yQIhftO0Kl","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:39.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550139853684832"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"entities":{"urls":[{"start":131,"end":154,"url":"https://t.co/lXrwHznQJT","expanded_url":"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47633396","display_url":"news.ycombinator.com/item?id=476333…","status":200,"title":"Anthropic no longer allowing Claude Code subscriptions to be used with OpenClaw | Hacker News","description":"Received the following email from Anthropic: Hi, Starting April 4 at 12pm PT / 8pm BST, you’ll no longer be able to use your Claude subscription limits for third-party harnesses including OpenClaw. You can still use them with your Claude account, but they will require extra usage, a pay-as-you-go option billed separatel y from your subscription. Your subscription still covers all Claude products, including Claude Code and Claude Cowork. To keep using third-party harnesses with your Claude login, turn on","unwound_url":"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47633396"}]},"author_id":"2038317470185082880","id":"2040550139757252749","text":"Tell HN: Anthropic no longer allowing Claude Code subscriptions to use OpenClaw。OpenClawで自動化してて思うのは、ツールの賢さより運用設計が先。みんなはどこから手をつけてる？ https://t.co/lXrwHznQJT","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:39.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550139757252749"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"entities":{"mentions":[{"start":13,"end":20,"username":"github","id":"13334762"},{"start":57,"end":69,"username":"AnthropicAI","id":"1353836358901501952"}]},"author_id":"1349090378708709376","id":"2040550130953158881","text":"The trending @GitHub repos aren't just an IP problem for @AnthropicAI — they're a supply chain problem for YOU.\n\n'chatgptprojects/claude-code' combines two brand names to imply legitimacy. Clone it, run it, and you're executing unverified code with access to your creds.\n\nTrending","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:37.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550130953158881"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"author_id":"1944000478754615300","id":"2040550122636157163","text":"Claude Opus 4.6 hallucinates 30% less on code reviews with Funnel-Aware Prompting.\n\nIt's chaining prompts to match the marketing funnel: Awareness → Interest → Desire → Action.\n\nDevs building AI agents: this structures your outputs for real workflows. Thread \uD83D\uDC47","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:35.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550122636157163"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"entities":{"mentions":[{"start":206,"end":214,"username":"bcherny","id":"159337660"}]},"author_id":"1601153790945771521","id":"2040550102897455322","text":"Been running Claude Code commando for a while, no predefined  /agents and no /skills calls wt occasional UI skill. I figured best way is to trust the model but augment with rigorous steering. Am I a psycho @bcherny ? Stairs  vs Escalator so I get steps in and fitter in future","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:30.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550102897455322"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":6},"entities":{"urls":[{"start":135,"end":158,"url":"https://t.co/xGI3b9WFRP","expanded_url":"http://Continue.dev","display_url":"Continue.dev","status":200,"title":"Quality control for your software factory. | Continue","description":"Source-controlled AI checks on every pull request. Standards as checks, enforced by AI, decided by humans.","unwound_url":"https://www.continue.dev/"},{"start":185,"end":208,"url":"https://t.co/nWogjm4oHM","expanded_url":"https://x.com/OMOUMAMA_AI/status/2040550067828867464/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/nWogjm4oHM","media_key":"3_2040550065211658240"}]},"author_id":"1669494102378024960","id":"2040550067828867464","text":"\uD83D\uDCF0 Anthropic、サードパーティハーネス（OpenClaw等）経由のClaude Code利用を有料化\n\nAnthropicが4月4日付で利用規約を更新し、$200/月のMaxサブスクリプションをClaude Code以外のサードパーティツール（OpenClaw、https://t.co/xGI3b9WFRP等）で使うことを禁止した。\n継続利用には「extra https://t.co/nWogjm4oHM","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:22.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550067828867464"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":9},"author_id":"2023598915367620608","id":"2040550053388128574","text":"今日のAIニュース 気になった3件\n\n① Claude Codeの料金体系変更\n→ AnthropicがOpenClawなど外部ツール連携に追加課金を開始。コーディング支援ツールのコスト構造が変化する可能性","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:18.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550053388128574"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"author_id":"1656823508826222592","id":"2040550048371491294","text":"Anthropic built Claude Code in 1.5 weeks...\n\nusing Claude Code itself.\n\nThat's the real story everyone's missing in the source code leak drama.","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:17.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550048371491294"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"author_id":"2033757173659156480","id":"2040550021603758465","text":"「最初はAIなんて信じられなかったケド、Claude Codeで1時間かかったデータ整理が5分で終了した瞬間にハマった！！ヤバい！！#AIの力」","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:11.000Z","entities":{"hashtags":[{"start":66,"end":71,"tag":"AIの力"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550021603758465"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"author_id":"2021960534908973056","id":"2040550019565293948","text":"よっしゃ、今日は作業できる！！\nこれはやらねば！！\n\n・自社商品用Xアカウント作成\n・note\n・動画作成\n・Claude Code 検証","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:10.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550019565293948"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":2},"entities":{"urls":[{"start":149,"end":172,"url":"https://t.co/3IOwiN3pmq","expanded_url":"https://luma.com/xb0d1wzr","display_url":"luma.com/xb0d1wzr","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2040550051181973505/bD0dXE0Z?format=jpg&name=orig","width":800,"height":419},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2040550051181973505/bD0dXE0Z?format=jpg&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"Notionユーザーが知るべき \"次の武器\" — Claude Codeで変わる仕事術 · Luma","description":"\uD83D\uDCA1 Notionだけでは届かない作業、ありませんか？ 請求書PDFの作成、Excelファイルの加工、フォルダやファイルの整理—— Notionをどれだけ使いこなしていても、「ローカルファイルの操作」だけは手作業のまま、という人は多いはず。 この勉強会では、Claude…","unwound_url":"https://luma.com/xb0d1wzr"}]},"author_id":"1641840893278961664","id":"2040550008643305699","text":"Notionユーザー向けClaude Code勉強会やります！\n\n体系的な講座や座学ではなく僕の実践知を共有する勉強会です。\n\nAI時代の情報基盤はNotionで揺るがない。それでもClaude Codeを使う理由がここにあります。\n\n第2, 3回も予定してますのでぜひ！\n参加申し込みはこちら\uD83D\uDC47\nhttps://t.co/3IOwiN3pmq","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:08.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550008643305699"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"1622781307666468872","id":"2040550007833776132","text":"日曜朝6時に気づいたこと。\n\nゴリラ、先週Claude Codeで「毎日の顧客データ集計」を自動化した。それまで毎朝30分かかってた業務。\n\n今は朝起きたらスクリプト走ってて、結果がSlackに届いてる。\n\nコード書けないゴリラでも「Claudeに日本語で指示→Claude","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:08.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550007833776132"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"1622781307666468872","id":"2040550006537781544","text":"毎日30分かかってた採用メール送信を、Claude Codeで完全自動化した。今は朝7時に自動実行。ゴリラはコード書けないのに、これが実現した話をする。","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:07.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550006537781544"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"entities":{"urls":[{"start":137,"end":160,"url":"https://t.co/11JhAF2pA3","expanded_url":"https://x.com/shingi_ai/status/2040549983674589693/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/11JhAF2pA3","media_key":"3_2040549981527085057"}]},"author_id":"1436121247889309698","id":"2040549983674589693","text":"Claude Codeが23年間誰にも気づかれなかったLinuxカーネルの脆弱性を発見した。しかも方法がシンプルすぎて、ソースコードを全ファイルにわたってスキャンさせただけらしい。Anthropicの研究者いわく「こんなの今まで一度も見つけたことない。でも今は山ほどある」 https://t.co/11JhAF2pA3","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:02.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549983674589693"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":1},"author_id":"2025678479254020097","id":"2040549982944526531","text":"Price hike on Anthropic's Claude Code? \n\nMore paywalls for users. Yet another barrier to entry for everyday coders. \n\nLet's focus on building tools people can actually use without breaking the bank.  \n\nKeeping most Coda One tools free isn't just a choice — it's a stance. \n\n#AI","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:02.000Z","entities":{"hashtags":[{"start":274,"end":277,"tag":"AI"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549982944526531"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":1},"author_id":"2028672153164587008","id":"2040549982357352662","text":"収益化まで遠回りする原因は、\n最初の2つです。\n\n1. ツールを増やしすぎる\n2. 売る前に作り込みすぎる\n\n非エンジニアの副業は、\nClaude Codeだけで小さく回して\n改善する方が速い。\n\n覚える量を減らすほど、\n継続率は上がります。\n\n共感したらリポストお願いします！","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:02.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549982357352662"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":1},"entities":{"urls":[{"start":108,"end":131,"url":"https://t.co/w5GJEd6QME","expanded_url":"https://qiita.com/joinclass/items/cc45d196d7f5b6613f50","display_url":"qiita.com/joinclass/item…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2040349213016350720/CWeyGChe?format=jpg&name=orig","width":1200,"height":630},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2040349213016350720/CWeyGChe?format=jpg&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"Claude Code Hooksの実践活用パターン5選 — 事故を防ぎ、品質を自動で守る仕組み - Qiita","description":"はじめに Claude Codeを業務で使い始めると、最初は「すごい、なんでもやってくれる」と感動する。だが1ヶ月も経つと「勝手にやりすぎて怖い」に変わる。 僕は一人法人でAIエージェント10部門を運用し、自動化率98%を達成している。その過程でgit push --fo...","unwound_url":"https://qiita.com/joinclass/items/cc45d196d7f5b6613f50"}],"hashtags":[{"start":143,"end":150,"tag":"Claude"},{"start":151,"end":156,"tag":"生成AI"}]},"author_id":"1797795278571089920","id":"2040549974661009497","text":"Claude Codeを「使いこなす」から「制御する」へ。git push --forceでブランチ消滅、おかしな敬語の営業メール送信…実際の事故から生まれたHooks活用パターン5選、めちゃくちゃ実践的でした。\n\nhttps://t.co/w5GJEd6QME\n\nvia Qiita #Claude #生成AI","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:00.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549974661009497"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"entities":{"urls":[{"start":59,"end":82,"url":"https://t.co/bwKkvev7P1","expanded_url":"https://aid.connpass.com/event/386203/?utm_campaign=event_participate_to_follower&utm_source=notifications&utm_medium=twitter","display_url":"aid.connpass.com/event/386203/?…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2040363378745708544/9kyCnAg8?format=jpg&name=orig","width":1280,"height":721},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2040363378745708544/9kyCnAg8?format=jpg&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"Claude Code Meetup Japan #4「Claude Code LT大会」 (2026/04/10 18:40〜)","description":"# Claude Code Meetup Japan #4 (「Claude Code LT大会」) ## 自律型エージェントが切り拓く、AI駆動開発の「新境地」 Claude CodeによるAI駆動開発の実践テクニック！！ 生成AI・LLMの登場からGitHub Copilot, Cursorをはじめとする開発ツールの登場により、コード生成・自動補完のみならず、要件整理、UIデザイン、設計、テスト作成、ドキュメント作成においてもAIを駆使する新たな開発スタイルが生まれつつあります。 更に「AI駆動要件定義」「AI駆動テスト」とも言える新たなパラダイムシフトにより、今後アプリケー...","unwound_url":"https://aid.connpass.com/event/386203/?utm_campaign=event_participate_to_follower&utm_source=notifications&utm_medium=twitter"}],"hashtags":[{"start":83,"end":100,"tag":"ClaudeCodeMeetup"}]},"author_id":"1710350522685992960","id":"2040549919199760841","text":"Claude Code Meetup Japan #4「Claude Code LT大会」 に参加を申し込みました！ https://t.co/bwKkvev7P1 #ClaudeCodeMeetup","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:59:46.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549919199760841"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":1},"author_id":"2036871992692137984","id":"2040549903584436300","text":"【知ってた？】Claude Codeは「プロンプト1つ」でLP・ブログ・ツールを自動生成できる。\nエンジニア不要、デザイン不要。この仕組みを副業に転用すると月10万円が現実的な数字になる。コードを書けなくても大丈夫。必要なのはAIへの\"正しい指示の出し方\"だけ。 #AI副業 #副業 #note副業","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:59:43.000Z","entities":{"hashtags":[{"start":132,"end":137,"tag":"AI副業"},{"start":138,"end":141,"tag":"副業"},{"start":142,"end":149,"tag":"note副業"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549903584436300"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"entities":{"mentions":[{"start":0,"end":7,"username":"trq212","id":"352806502"}],"urls":[{"start":69,"end":92,"url":"https://t.co/j59bv2swTb","expanded_url":"https://x.com/Peacerful/status/2040549673002303921/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/j59bv2swTb","media_key":"3_2040549521919205376"}]},"author_id":"1283325128655482880","id":"2040549673002303921","text":"@trq212 can you please add latex support in claude code and cowork ? https://t.co/j59bv2swTb","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:58:48.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549673002303921"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"2033469843081715712","id":"2040549479015674054","text":"ハヴァーツがゴール決めてる間に、わたしはClaude Codeでバグと格闘してた。\n\n非エンジニアがコード書く時代、\nプロ選手がゴール決めるより難易度低いかも。\n\n#ハヴァーツ","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:58:02.000Z","entities":{"hashtags":[{"start":82,"end":88,"tag":"ハヴァーツ"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549479015674054"]},{"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"entities":{"urls":[{"start":110,"end":133,"url":"https://t.co/fXy3aMd4HN","expanded_url":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/697623f8000000000b01153e","display_url":"xiaohongshu.com/explore/697623…","unwound_url":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/404/sec_cykvuTFm?redirectPath=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xiaohongshu.com%2Fexplore%2F697623f8000000000b01153e&error_code=300031&error_msg=%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%